{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A Mischievous Cat Led Me to Develop a Relaxing Puzzle Game! \ud83d\udc31\u2728</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Speaking of inspiration for this game, I must tell you about my adorable Pipi! A white cat who's both beautiful and naughty! \ud83e\udd0d</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330220/extras/pp-2016_09_08_13.jpg?t=1740078772\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330220/extras/pp-2013_05_29_4.jpg?t=1740078772\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Look at this cutie! Usually so peaceful and heart-melting... BUT!!!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">My heart skips a beat every time I see them crouching at the table edge, pawing at things! \ud83d\ude31</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">And that innocent face!! That's the expression they make after causing chaos! So annoying yet adorable!!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330220/extras/pp-2010_11_20_18.jpg?t=1740078772\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Inspired by my daily &quot;torment&quot; (just kidding) from Pipi, I developed &quot;Magic Puzzle King 2: Rolling Cat&quot; \ud83c\udfae</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330220/extras/0009.png?t=1740078772\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Super fun game concept:<br>\u2728 The protagonist is a mischievous cat (based on Pipi, of course!)<br>\u2728 Levels designed around cats and their furry friends<br>\u2728 Each level features items broken by our feline overlords<br>\u2728 Players solve puzzles to restore the broken items</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Game features:<br>\ud83c\udfaf Progressive difficulty, 15 levels from easy to challenging<br>\ud83c\udfb5 Soothing music for stress relief<br>\ud83c\udf08 Fresh artistic style with adorable cats<br>\ud83c\udfae Simple controls, fun for all ages</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Special highlights:<br>\ud83d\udc9d Cute cats randomly appear to &quot;help&quot; you solve puzzles<br>\ud83d\udc9d Base game with 15 levels completely free<br>\ud83d\udc9d Multiple DLCs featuring cats and their adorable friends, plus extra levels</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">From a cat servant tortured by my feline master to a game developer - I guess this is what cat ownership leads to! \ud83e\udd70</p>","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/3330220?t=1740078772","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330220/page_bg_raw.jpg?t=1740078772","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330220/30dfa5e00c1adfe9525450152c1a90753f40ca2d/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1740078772","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330220/30dfa5e00c1adfe9525450152c1a90753f40ca2d/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1740078772","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A Mischievous Cat Led Me to Develop a Relaxing Puzzle Game! \ud83d\udc31\u2728</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Speaking of inspiration for this game, I must tell you about my adorable Pipi! A white cat who's both beautiful and naughty! \ud83e\udd0d</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330220/extras/pp-2016_09_08_13.jpg?t=1740078772\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330220/extras/pp-2013_05_29_4.jpg?t=1740078772\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Look at this cutie! Usually so peaceful and heart-melting... BUT!!!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">My heart skips a beat every time I see them crouching at the table edge, pawing at things! \ud83d\ude31</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">And that innocent face!! That's the expression they make after causing chaos! So annoying yet adorable!!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330220/extras/pp-2010_11_20_18.jpg?t=1740078772\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Inspired by my daily &quot;torment&quot; (just kidding) from Pipi, I developed &quot;Magic Puzzle King 2: Rolling Cat&quot; \ud83c\udfae</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330220/extras/0009.png?t=1740078772\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Super fun game concept:<br>\u2728 The protagonist is a mischievous cat (based on Pipi, of course!)<br>\u2728 Levels designed around cats and their furry friends<br>\u2728 Each level features items broken by our feline overlords<br>\u2728 Players solve puzzles to restore the broken items</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Game features:<br>\ud83c\udfaf Progressive difficulty, 15 levels from easy to challenging<br>\ud83c\udfb5 Soothing music for stress relief<br>\ud83c\udf08 Fresh artistic style with adorable cats<br>\ud83c\udfae Simple controls, fun for all ages</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Special highlights:<br>\ud83d\udc9d Cute cats randomly appear to &quot;help&quot; you solve puzzles<br>\ud83d\udc9d Base game with 15 levels completely free<br>\ud83d\udc9d Multiple DLCs featuring cats and their adorable friends, plus extra levels</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">From a cat servant tortured by my feline master to a game developer - I guess this is what cat ownership leads to! \ud83e\udd70</p>","developers":["Magic Cat"],"genres":[{"description":"Casual","id":"4"},{"description":"Free To Play","id":"37"}],"header_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_i